<section class="om-headspace">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h2>OM HEADSPACE</h2>
      <p>Head spacer er en forening hvor unge frivillige hjælper andre unge. Vi tilbyder en lav tærskel for unge der har brug for nogen at tale med om deres problemer og følelser.</p>
      <a href="/info" class="btn-green">› Læs mere om os her</a>
    </div>
    <div class="illustration">
      <img src="/images/pigeVindue.webp" class="photo-layer" alt="headspace" />
      <svg width="465" height="435" viewBox="0 0 465 435" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
        <rect y="64.8943" width="410.538" height="374.666" transform="rotate(-9.09497 0 64.8943)" fill="url(#pattern0_646_1339)"></rect>
        <defs>
          <pattern id="pattern0_646_1339" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
            <use xlink:href="#image0_646_1339" transform="scale(0.00194175 0.00212766)"></use>
          </pattern>
          <image
            id="image0_646_1339"
            width="515"
            height="470"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
            xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"
          />
        </defs>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .om-headspace {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 60px 32px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--green);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  p {
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .btn-green {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    background: var(--green);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-green:hover {
    background: var(--green-highlight);
  }

  .illustration {
    position: relative;
    height: 440px;
  }

  /* Back layer: photo, rotated the opposite way */
  .photo-layer {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 0;
    width: 80%;
    height: 95%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border-radius: 14px;
    transform: rotate(4deg);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  /* Front layer: SVG illustration, rotated over the photo */
  .illustration svg {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 65%;
    max-width: 240px;
    transform: rotate(-9deg);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18));
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .illustration {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
